title: Triffet, Carrie
description:
Carrie Triffet hears the Voice of Spirit. Long Time No See traces her unlikely journey through Orthodox Jewish beginnings and 20 years of Buddhist practice, to a wholly unexpected awakening in 2005 that changes everything.
Join Carrie on this true-life odyssey, which begins in the Midwest and travels to sunny California by way of London, Paris, and Sedona, Arizona. Learn the metaphysical lessons offered by a swanky Vegas hotel room and a past-life crime scene (among many others), as Carrie relays the messages of universal truth she is given to share with us all.
